<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6009">‌مَحْمُودُ بْنُ خَالِدٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6833">‌الْوَلِيدُ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> فَتَوَضَّأَ ثَلَاثًا ثَلَاثًا، وَغَسَلَ رِجْلَيْهِ، بِغَيْرِ عَدَدٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>